data.description: This charming home offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort, with easy access to major highways and all necessities just minutes away. Step inside to discover an inviting open floorplan, where every corner is bathed in natural light. Say goodbye to carpet woes - this home boasts sleek tile flooring throughout, making maintenance a breeze.The spacious living area is ideal for relaxing or entertaining guests, while the adjoining kitchen isthoughtfully designed with ample counter space, allowing for effortless meal preparation and culinary creativity. Inside, you'll also appreciate the elegant touches, like coffered ceilings that add a touch of sophistication to the space. One of the highlights of this home is its large backyard, providing endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment and customization. Whether you dream of creating a lush garden oasis or setting up a play area for the kids, this expansive outdoor space has you covered.
